Package org.dmd.dms.generated.dmo

Class Summary
ActionDefinitionDMO This class is used to define the actions that may be triggered on an object.
AttributeDefinitionDMO This class is used to define attributes to be used as part of a class definition.
ClassDefinitionDMO This class provides the basic mechanism to define new classes for a schema.
DmsDefinitionDMO The DmsDefinition class provides a common base for all definition classes.
DmwWrapperDMO The DmwWrapper class is the basis for all server-side objects that wrapper Dark Matter Obects and extend them with behaviour
EnumDefinitionDMO The EnumDefinition allows for the definition of real Java enums that provide inherent mapping of the string and integer values of the enum into actual enum values.
SchemaDefinitionDMO This class is used to define a schema as a discrete, nameable entity.
TypeDefinitionDMO The TypeDefinition is used to define the types of attributes that can be used as the basis for attribute values.
